        "created_at": "2022-04-25T15:05:13.034Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I basically run the dr_agent manually inside the pod.<br>\nFor now, I run it in the proxy and some log pods. It seems ok.<br>\nAnother interesting thing I see is the more storageserverperpods I put in, the better the performance to achieve sync up between the db but it is not linear.  For 2 per pods, I got 2x faster, but with 3 per pods, I got 2.8 times faster.</p>",
